rComments: One of the most amazing professors I've ever had. He's so nice and so kind. Willing to do everything to make sure you have a good mark. Super helpful powerpoints. Good at explaining. Funny. Weekly quizzes that are easy. Take this class. Loved it.

Prof Restrepo is not a great prof. He doesn't explain things very well and only uses the textbook. I didn't properly learn the material in this course and was often left confused. His teaching would be better if he used powerpoints and gave examples of the material.
